node.text:
I didn’t even wanna celebrate this year.. just was focused on some other personal things & goals but I’m happy @emilyb_ didn’t listen to me & threw me a surprise party. I get to party for work but this was a good time i didn’t know i needed.. good company i hadn’t been around in a while… and a good cause, bcuz my 1st album is such a part of me & my career.. And even the date reminds me of being able to find light in dark times. 

Salute everyone who played a part in making it happen, especially @mznatina, @iamcharlenethomas, & my label @defjam.  @ciroc, @deleontequila, @alfakher.usa, @june_florist_wedding_events appreciate your support!! Shoutout my sneaky ass Team for keeping the Surprise a Surprise 😂 THE FAMILY 4 LIFE 🖤💯🤟🏾 [shot by @drevinciwrks]

Beach + Convertible S Class Benz + @goldenbarbie = Video 

Fun Fact : This video came about from just chilling at Taj crib wit some friends & in between J’s & a few drinks we decided to wake up the next morning & shoot something. And what better video to shoot other then the song wit the title that got us to thinking.. Mad random but a vibe (in my most NYC accent 😂)

node.text:
I didn’t even wanna celebrate this year.. just was focused on some other personal things & goals but I’m happy @emilyb_ didn’t listen to me & threw me a surprise party. I get to party for work but this was a good time i didn’t know i needed.. good company i hadn’t been around in a while… and a good cause, bcuz my 1st album is such a part of me & my career.. And even the date reminds me of being able to find light in dark times. 

Salute everyone who played a part in making it happen, especially @mznatina, @iamcharlenethomas, & my label @defjam.  @ciroc, @deleontequila, @alfakher.usa, @june_florist_wedding_events appreciate your support!! Shoutout my sneaky ass Team for keeping the Surprise a Surprise 😂 THE FAMILY 4 LIFE 🖤💯🤟🏾 [shot by @drevinciwrks]

node.text:
They got me!! Last night @emilyb_ & @defjam threw me a surprise party to celebrate the 20 Year Anniversary of my 1st Album GHETTO FABOLOUS!!!

I thought i was going to a NYFW gig.. 😂 And i was mad bcuz they told me when i got there they didn’t have my 💰 & they had to wire it Tuesday! 😡

But i finally had my 1st Surprise Party! Instantly changed my mood & energy and i ended up having a good time!! A lot of family & friends who have been along wit me on this journey came thru to celebrate with me & i appreciate them all!!

But my advice, any other surprise y’all plan.. don’t play wit my bag💰Cuz i almost said fuck this shit & told the driver take me home and woulda missed my own party 😂😂😂😂

#GhetttoFabTurns20 💿

20 Year Anniversary!! 💿
GHETTO FABOLOUS 

Sept. 11th 2001 

Love to everyone who supported this effort & has been on this journey with me. I was just a little dude wit a big dream… Figuring it out & tryna make the transition.. And the love the world showed me & my craft made my 1st Album a Platinum one.. Appreciate everyone who had a hand in this album, as it was a confirmation to myself that i had something.. And when a person figures out they GOT SOMETHING.. That’s when you become who you were meant to be! 🖤
